				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The party has stopped to camp for the first time. The player can speak to Shadowheart as they rest. She restates the urgent need to find a healer who can help them with their tadpole problem. If the player elected to confide in other party members ahead of her she'll caution that they may not be trustworthy."
